@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container about-section">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="mb-4 display-4">About WanderVibe</h2>
            <p class="lead">Welcome to <span class="highlight">WanderVibe</span> - Your Ultimate Travel Companion!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>At WanderVibe, we believe that travel is more than just a journey; it's a way to explore new horizons, create lasting memories, and experience the world in all its glory. Whether you're a solo adventurer, a couple looking for a romantic getaway, or a family planning the vacation of a lifetime, WanderVibe is here to make your travel dreams come true.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1682687220742-aba13b6e50ba?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Travel Image" class="img-fluid rounded animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
            <p>Our mission is to provide seamless and enriching travel experiences that cater to all your needs. From booking flights and hotels to discovering hidden gems and local attractions, WanderVibe is your go-to platform for all things travel. We strive to offer personalized services that ensure every journey is unforgettable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1469854523086-cc02fe5d8800?q=80&w=2021&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Adventure Image" class="img-fluid rounded animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row text-center mb-3">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3 display-6"><strong>Why Choose WanderVibe?</strong></h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card mb-4 animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title highlight">Comprehensive Travel Solutions</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">One-stop platform for flights, hotels, and experiences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card mb-4 animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title highlight">Expert Recommendations</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Insider tips and curated travel guides.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card mb-4 animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title highlight">24/7 Customer Support</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Assistance anytime, anywhere.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card mb-4 animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title highlight">Best Price Guarantee</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Competitive pricing for unbeatable value.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>We are dedicated to providing exceptional service and support throughout your travel journey. Our team of travel experts is passionate about helping you explore the world and ensuring that every trip is a delightful experience. We value your feedback and continuously strive to improve our services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605152276897-4f618f831968?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Support Image" class="img-fluid rounded animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 text-center">
            <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3 display-6"><strong>Get in Touch</strong></h4>
            <p>Ready to embark on your next adventure? Browse through our extensive range of travel options and start planning today. For any inquiries or assistance, feel free to contact our friendly support team. We are here to help you make the most of your travel experiences.</p>
            <p class="mt-4">Thank you for choosing WanderVibe - Where Every Journey Begins!</p>
            <a href="/Home/Contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-3 animate__animated animate__pulse animate__infinite">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
